                            <comment id="14454411" author="godin" created="Sat, 11 Apr 2009 20:02:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This can be done by using one suite file from another:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;MainSuite.xml&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;!DOCTYPE suite SYSTEM &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;http://testng.org/testng-1.0.dtd&quot;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;suite name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;MainSuite&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;suite-files&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;suite-file path=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;ExampleTestSuite.xml&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;suite-file path=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;AnotherTestSuite.xml&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/suite-files&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/suite&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14454784" author="krosenvold" created="Wed, 19 Jan 2011 15:00:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed (with test) in r1060988&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
